# Reproduce bugs with tests only

- when asked to reproduce a bug (or to "repro first", "repro the issue"), **do not change production code**
- add or adjust **only tests** that demonstrate the bug (e.g. a test that asserts the desired behaviour and fails on current code)
- production changes (fixes, refactors, new APIs) come **after** the failing test is in place and agreed

```text
Repro step: 0 production changes. Only new/updated test(s) that fail and document the bug.
Fix step:  only after repro is confirmed, implement the fix so the test goes green.
```
